{"id": 252, "genre": 1001, "title": "你身上应验过的墨菲定律？", "description": "“墨菲定律”是一种心理学效应：“你有一种奇怪的体质，世界上的蠢事都会发生在你身上”。现在呢，我们要来探讨一个严肃的商业问题……你身上应验过的墨菲定律有哪些？", "record_count": 2576, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606071945495nSezDfdH3qlu1a7.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-02-05T07:02:25Z", "options": [{"id": 1740, "content": "如果我爱他，肯定会被他甩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 1742, "content": "喜欢我的我不喜欢，我喜欢的不喜欢我", "image": null, "praise_count": 127, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 1741, "content": "最不想发生的发生了。", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200745aeNxzcgVUGjK2w4v", "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 1871, "content": "每当感觉我们很近却发现更远了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 1700, "content": "越活越穷，是这个么意思么？", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200745pDqReZLNS14ghBUo.jpg", "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 44}, {"id": 1705, "content": "看完恐怖片就会觉得上厕所很有压力", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200745XGtEzsk3xT9W54ni.jpg", "praise_count": 102, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3660}, {"id": 1706, "content": "穿坏的，遗失的一定是自己最喜欢的衣服，比如一件timberland的长绒棉衬衫，回想再三，肯定是出差（都是带自己最喜欢穿的衣服）的时候在酒店退房忘记拿了。至于那些不喜欢的衣服，除非刻意扔掉他们，１０多年都过去了还静静躺在我的衣柜角落里。", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 62703}, {"id": 2807, "content": "面对对开的门，我选择的那面总是锁住的。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 1795, "content": "加载不出来的网页在点╳后那一瞬打开了", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193855GRPqf28yp9QWzg05.jgp", "praise_count": 234, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 76475}, {"id": 1806, "content": " 别叫我。。。然后老师就叫你了。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 143, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2280, "content": "不错啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4576}, {"id": 2281, "content": "有意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4576}, {"id": 2282, "content": "不错", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234724t9Mj3npKAXJlyNeq.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4576}, {"id": 2283, "content": "不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112282}, {"id": 1731, "content": "洗车的第二天必下雨", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 1643, "content": "刚过保修期的第二天东西就会坏掉", "image": "img/option/option/201607022007442j8g4rU5Y3LaStzO.jpg", "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 177154, "content": "不想被抽到说时政，不想被抽到说时政，然后偏偏抽到了我?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957931}, {"id": 2307, "content": "好啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112517}, {"id": 2308, "content": "喝喝", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234722IPwsD5XA9ZVTzufW.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112517}, {"id": 178180, "content": "怎么说？不会说啊！哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/20170313103124krh3HzUKsFLvBYjq", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 968481}, {"id": 3089, "content": "刚洗完头一定会被雨淋\r\n\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 219410, "content": "我看好的情侣一定会分手（已经三对了 真事）\n跟我告白的男生不久后会被告白（摊手）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069400}, {"id": 266260, "content": "一出国必撞大姨妈 连着三次了我不得不服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 710492}, {"id": 326421, "content": "已经计划好的，一定会被突然出现的人或事破坏掉…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576265}, {"id": 1814, "content": "在一个人面前做了丢脸的事之后，我总觉得他在跟踪我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 174614, "content": "出门一定会带伞   一定会带钱    手机  耳机    有条件还可以带个充电宝       一定会买瓶矿泉水     还有一包纸(有时候突然就流鼻血了)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957757}, {"id": 226839, "content": "最坏的事情总在最好的时间发生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095222}, {"id": 197660, "content": "我喜欢的人永远在我不喜欢她以后才喜欢我(눈_눈)", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016594}, {"id": 230940, "content": "一直不想发生的事，却总是在我一直想着它的时候发生了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079779}, {"id": 228125, "content": "梦中梦见科幻片\n梦中梦见曾经丢失的东西在何处", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082191}, {"id": 340766, "content": "\n比预想的最差结果还要差", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644053}, {"id": 1823, "content": "戴帽子就不刮风，刚摘下帽子立马刮风！", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200745L2FlKXuiY9MEz1pn.jgp", "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 77974}, {"id": 201760, "content": "装逼必失败", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007440}, {"id": 339240, "content": "等了很长时间，喜欢的人还是没给我发信息，结果睡着之后又给我发了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555562}, {"id": 174121, "content": "每次到最后二选一的时候，总是选中不该选的那个。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956297}, {"id": 2347, "content": "不错啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113336}, {"id": 202542, "content": "一追姑娘，她就想跟我当朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028908}, {"id": 239408, "content": "总是在放假的时候下雨", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145257}, {"id": 2099, "content": "好", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234724Uevy6AI1afxo7cDj.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1}, {"id": 254520, "content": "刚放进口袋里的烟瞬间回头找不见了！？口袋虫洞？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213317}, {"id": 178237, "content": "觉得正在进行的场景梦中一模一样地出现过", "image": "img/option/option/20170313120335uhUmWIDgHZR4fOkB", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 968587}, {"id": 195389, "content": "哇我这次考的好好哦！成绩出来后就是狗屎。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 975434}, {"id": 227136, "content": "控制不住语气(´ﾟдﾟ`)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 990667}, {"id": 175171, "content": "每次洗头换衣服必变天。差点信了邪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958192}, {"id": 175431, "content": "在在乎的人面前出糗，终生难忘的那种糗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949127}, {"id": 178503, "content": "总是在领导着急要东西的时候电脑卡住。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970055}, {"id": 1868, "content": "想见的人永远见不到，不想见的人随时看得到", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 85306}, {"id": 1869, "content": "周一到周五每天都觉得长，周末却很快过完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 1870, "content": "明明是我很重要的好友，却突然删了我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 210002, "content": "复习了一个月考试发下试卷才发现复习重点搞错了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1048545}]}